<!-- ── PROBLEM ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="problem">
  <div class="problem-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">The Challenge</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">DOI Compliance is<br>Still a Manual Nightmare</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom:32px">
        Every year, government departments waste thousands of hours chasing employees
        for paper forms, managing spreadsheets, and scrambling before audit deadlines.
        There has to be a better way.
      </p>
      <a href="@Url.Action("RequestDemo","DemoRequest")" class="btn btn-primary" style="background:var(--navy)">
        See the Declarify Solution →
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-cards reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="pc-icon">📄</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pc-title">Paper-Based & Error-Prone</div>
          <div class="pc-desc">Manual forms get lost, misfiled, or submitted with incomplete information — creating audit risk and compliance gaps.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="pc-icon warn">⏰</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pc-title">Missed Deadlines & Low Return Rates</div>
          <div class="pc-desc">Without automated reminders, compliance officers spend weeks following up individually. Average return rates drop below 60%.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="pc-icon blue">🔍</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pc-title">No Real-Time Visibility</div>
          <div class="pc-desc">Managers have no live dashboard. They only discover compliance gaps when auditors arrive — too late to act.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="pc-icon">🗄️</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pc-title">Verification is Manual & Slow</div>
          <div class="pc-desc">Cross-checking employee declarations against CIPC records or credit databases takes weeks and consumes significant budget.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── FEATURES ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="features-inner">
    <div class="features-header reveal">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Platform Features</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything You Need for<br>DOI Compliance</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="color:var(--muted)">Purpose-built for South African public sector requirements. Not a generic form tool — a specialist compliance engine.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="feat-icon">📤</div>
        <div class="feat-title">Smart Bulk Requests</div>
        <div class="feat-desc">Send DOI requests to hundreds of employees in one click. Each receives a unique, secure, time-bound link. Automated email reminders escalate as deadlines approach.</div>
        <span class="feat-tag">Saves 70% admin time</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="feat-icon">📊</div>
        <div class="feat-title">Real-Time Compliance Dashboard</div>
        <div class="feat-desc">Live visibility into every employee's status. Filter by department, overdue, submitted, reviewed. Export audit-ready reports instantly with one click.</div>
        <span class="feat-tag">95% completion rates</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="feat-icon">✍️</div>
        <div class="feat-title">Digital Attestation & Signatures</div>
        <div class="feat-desc">Legally binding digital signatures on all submissions. Complete PDF generation for each declaration — ready for audit without any additional work.</div>
        <span class="feat-tag">Audit-ready PDFs</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="feat-icon">🎨</div>
        <div class="feat-title">Custom Form Templates</div>
        <div class="feat-desc">Build any DOI template using our drag-and-drop field builder. Supports text, dropdowns, file uploads, signatures, and conditional logic. Pre-loaded City of Johannesburg template included.</div>
        <span class="feat-tag">Fully configurable</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="feat-icon">🔍</div>
        <div class="feat-title">CIPC & Credit Verification</div>
        <div class="feat-desc">Integrated directorship lookups and credit checks via external API. Cross-reference employee declarations against official records to surface undisclosed conflicts automatically.</div>
        <span class="feat-tag">External verification</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="feat-icon">📎</div>
        <div class="feat-title">Document Uploads & Evidence</div>
        <div class="feat-desc">Employees attach supporting documents (ID, certificates, financial statements) directly to their submission. Reviewers access everything in one place — no email chains.</div>
        <span class="feat-tag">Centralised evidence</span>
      </div>

      <div class="feat-big reveal">
        <div>
          <div class="feat-big-icon">👥</div>
          <div class="feat-big-title">Built-In Review Workflow</div>
          <div class="feat-big-desc">
            Declarify is end-to-end. Once an employee submits, their line manager receives instant notification
            and can review, approve, request amendments, or trigger external verification — all within the platform.
            Every action is logged with a digital signature and timestamp for full auditability.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feat-big-checks">
          <div class="fbc"><div class="fbc-dot">✓</div><div class="fbc-text">Multi-level review chain — employee → line manager → compliance officer</div></div>
          <div class="fbc"><div class="fbc-dot">✓</div><div class="fbc-text">Reviewer notes and private annotations visible only to management</div></div>
          <div class="fbc"><div class="fbc-dot">✓</div><div class="fbc-text">Amendment workflow — request changes without rejecting the full submission</div></div>
          <div class="fbc"><div class="fbc-dot">✓</div><div class="fbc-text">Task status history — full audit trail of every status change and who made it</div></div>
          <div class="fbc"><div class="fbc-dot">✓</div><div class="fbc-text">Communication centre — secure threaded messaging between employees and compliance team</div></div>
          <div class="fbc"><div class="fbc-dot">✓</div><div class="fbc-text">Credit-based verification — only pay for CIPC/credit checks you actually run</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── HOW IT WORKS ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="how" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="how-inner">
    <div class="how-header reveal">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Simple Process</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">From Setup to <span class="accent">95% Compliance</span><br>in Four Steps</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">No lengthy implementations. No IT projects. You can be live and sending requests the same day.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="step-num-wrap"><div class="step-num">1</div></div>
        <div class="step-title">Onboard Your Organisation</div>
        <div class="step-desc">Import employees via CSV or add manually. Configure your email domain, departments, and manager hierarchy. Takes under 30 minutes.</div>
        <span class="step-badge">Same-day setup</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="step-num-wrap"><div class="step-num">2</div></div>
        <div class="step-title">Build Your DOI Template</div>
        <div class="step-desc">Use our pre-built City of Johannesburg template or customise your own. Every field type supported — including file uploads and digital signatures.</div>
        <span class="step-badge">Pre-loaded templates</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="step-num-wrap"><div class="step-num">3</div></div>
        <div class="step-title">Send Bulk Requests</div>
        <div class="step-desc">Select all employees or filter by department. Set the due date. Click send. Each employee receives a unique secure link via email. Automatic reminders handle the follow-up.</div>
        <span class="step-badge">One click to all staff</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <div class="step-num-wrap"><div class="step-num">4</div></div>
        <div class="step-title">Review, Verify & Report</div>
        <div class="step-desc">Watch your compliance rate climb in real time. Review submissions, trigger verification checks, and generate audit-ready PDF reports — all from one dashboard.</div>
        <span class="step-badge">Audit-ready instantly</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── SECURITY ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="security" id="security">
  <div class="security-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Enterprise Security</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Government-Grade Security,<br>Certified & Verified</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom:28px">
        Declarify was built from the ground up for sensitive public sector data.
        Every architectural decision prioritises security, auditability, and data sovereignty.
      </p>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom:32px">
        Your data stays on your servers. Declarify supports self-hosted deployment,
        meaning no sensitive declarations ever leave your infrastructure.
      </p>
      <a href="@Url.Action("RequestDemo","DemoRequest")" class="btn btn-primary" style="background:var(--navy)">
        Request a Security Briefing →
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="security-grid reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="sec-card">
        <span class="sec-icon">🔐</span>
        <div class="sec-title">AES-256 Encryption</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">All sensitive data encrypted at rest using AES-256-CBC with HMAC-SHA256 integrity checks. Keys are never stored with data.</div>
        <span class="sec-badge">✓ Active</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-card">
        <span class="sec-icon">🔑</span>
        <div class="sec-title">HMAC-SHA256 API Auth</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">Every API request is signed with a per-company HMAC key derived via PBKDF2. Timestamp + nonce prevents replay attacks.</div>
        <span class="sec-badge">✓ Active</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-card">
        <span class="sec-icon">📋</span>
        <div class="sec-title">Full Audit Trail</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">Every action — submission, review, amendment, status change — is logged with actor identity, timestamp, and digital signature.</div>
        <span class="sec-badge">✓ Immutable</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-card">
        <span class="sec-icon">🛡️</span>
        <div class="sec-title">POPIA Compliant</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">Built for South Africa's Protection of Personal Information Act. Data minimisation, consent tracking, and subject access request support.</div>
        <span class="sec-badge">✓ Certified</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-card">
        <span class="sec-icon">🏠</span>
        <div class="sec-title">Self-Hosted Deployment</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">Deploy on your own government servers or approved cloud. Full data sovereignty — employee data never leaves your infrastructure.</div>
        <span class="sec-badge">✓ Your servers</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-card">
        <span class="sec-icon">⚡</span>
        <div class="sec-title">Rate Limiting & DDoS</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">Per-company API rate limiting, security headers (X-Frame, CSP, HSTS), and input sanitisation on all endpoints by default.</div>
        <span class="sec-badge">✓ Active</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

