<!-- ── FAQ ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="faq" id="faq">
  <div class="faq-inner">
    <div class="faq-header reveal">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Common Questions</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything You Need to Know</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      @foreach (var item in new (string Q, string A)[] {
        ("What is a Declaration of Interest and why does it matter?",
         "A Declaration of Interest (DOI) is a formal disclosure by a public servant of any personal, financial, or other interest that could influence their official duties. Under South African legislation including the Public Service Regulations and MFMA, government employees are legally required to submit these annually. Failure to comply exposes the organisation to audit findings, governance risk, and potential disciplinary action."),
        ("How long does it take to go live with Declarify?",
         "Most organisations are fully operational the same day. After a brief onboarding session, you import your employee list via CSV, activate the pre-built DOI template, and send your first bulk request. There is no lengthy IT deployment required for the cloud-hosted version. Self-hosted deployments typically take 2–3 days with technical support included."),
        ("How does the credit system work? What does a credit cost?",
         "Credits are used for form submissions and external verification checks (CIPC lookups, credit bureau queries). You purchase credits in advance and only consume them when employees submit forms or you initiate a verification check. Basic form submissions use 1 credit each. Verification checks vary by type. Credits expire after 12 months. There are no monthly subscription fees — you pay only for what you use."),
        ("Is our employee data safe? Where is it stored?",
         "Declarify supports full self-hosted deployment on your own government servers. All sensitive fields are encrypted at rest using AES-256-CBC. All data in transit is encrypted via TLS 1.3. The system is POPIA compliant and includes subject access request support. In self-hosted mode, no data ever leaves your infrastructure."),
        ("Can Declarify handle multiple departments and large employee counts?",
         "Yes. Declarify is designed for organisations with hundreds to thousands of employees. You can structure employees by department, assign multiple managers, set department-level compliance targets, and generate per-department reports. Bulk requests can be targeted to the full organisation or filtered subsets."),
        ("What happens if an employee misses the deadline?",
         "Declarify sends automated email reminders at intervals you configure (e.g., 7 days before, 3 days before, on deadline day). After the deadline, overdue employees are flagged on your dashboard and their status is highlighted for escalation. You can send manual follow-up communications directly from the platform's built-in messaging centre."),
        ("Does Declarify integrate with our existing HR system?",
         "Employee data import is handled via a standard CSV upload that maps to your HR system's export format. We do not require a live API integration with your HR system to operate. Custom integrations can be scoped as part of an enterprise engagement.")
      }) {
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            @item.Q
            <svg class="faq-chevron" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-a">@item.A</div>
        </div>
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

